{"tid":2397429,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(6/2)政府就土瓜灣華發大廈作出限制與檢測宣告及強制檢測公告","createTime":"2021-02-06T12:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T12:09:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2fdfe4c79d381a1b9118d4472c62e9aed1b30f3a","tid":2397429,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/06/P2021020600731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F06%2FP2021020600731.htm&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIcQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=df6da6e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/06/P2021020600731.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a2cbe2262f9d74a351a9aa3266a6a066d730f48d","tid":2397429,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"政府今日（二月六日）引用《預防及控制疾病（對若干人士強制檢測）規例》（第599J章），作出限制與檢測宣告（下稱「相關宣告」），自下午八時起限制在土瓜灣指明「受限區域」（即土瓜灣馬坑涌道4-6號華發大廈，見附件）內的人士（下稱受檢人士）須留在其處所並接受強制檢測。受檢人士須在其處所等候，直至區內所有已識別的受檢人士完成檢測，而相關檢測結果亦已獲大致確定，方可離開其處所。"},{"pid":"e52ce14ca226b24d466ceda2aabf7a9416305f47","tid":2397429,"uid":369011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQryrMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQryrMe.jpg&h=e71aeb33&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}